        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-04-17 16:34:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 10:\n\nHi,\n\nCould you please review these changes? They refer to SDC-2499, which fixes many of the problems related to the testing of asdctool. It is part of a topic which goal is to separate the report writing and formatting logic to improve maintainability and testability.\n\nThis first set of modifications regroups everything needed to remove the static global shared state of the ValidationConfigManager class.\n\nThank you for your help and mentoring.\n\nFrancis.",
        "patchset_number": 10
      },
